hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I hate shopping viagra contrareembolso Y'all "compassionate conservatives" DO NOT support the actual people in the military. If you did, you would be telling your elected representatives to NOT cut funding for VA hospitals, to NOT cut funding for SNAP, to NOT cut funding for Tricare, to NOT table legislation that would help military veterans find civilian jobs. But you all don't freaking CARE about any actual people beyond yourselves. As long as you've got yours, who gives a flying F at a doughnut what other people may be going through?
